Class MapillarySquareDownloadManagerThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • org.openstreetmap.josm.plugins.mapillary.downloads.MapillarySquareDownloadManagerThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class MapillarySquareDownloadManagerThread
extends java.lang.Thread
    This Class is needed to create an indeterminate amount of downloads, because the Mapillary API has a parameter called page which is needed when the amount of requested images is quite big.
